---

---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-6 whitespace-nowrap tracking-wide text-[#544A40]">
                あなたに合わせたレッスンを
            </h2>
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-[#A88B58] text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] font-serif uppercase"
            >
                <div class="h-[1px] w-10 bg-[#A88B58]/40"></div>
                Personalized Lesson
                <div class="h-[1px] w-10 bg-[#A88B58]/40"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-16">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-[1px] border-[#A88B58]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#A88B58]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-7 h-7"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-[17px] font-medium text-[#544A40] mb-5 font-serif tracking-widest">
                    初心者の方も安心
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[15px] leading-loose text-[#6B5F54]">
                    楽譜が読めなくても大丈夫です。<br />
                    <span class="inline-block">基礎から丁寧に、</span><span
                        class="inline-block">あなたのペースに合わせて</span
                    ><span class="inline-block">サポートいたします。</span>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-[1px] border-[#A88B58]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#A88B58]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-7 h-7"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-[17px] font-medium text-[#544A40] mb-5 font-serif tracking-widest">
                    年齢不問
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[15px] leading-loose text-[#6B5F54]">
                    大人の初心者・再開者の方を中心に、シニアの方やお子さまのレッスンもご相談いただけます。<br />
                    <span class="inline-block"
                        >「弾きたい」と思ったその時が、始めどきです。</span
                    ><span class="inline-block">年齢制限はありません。</span>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <div
                    class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-[1px] border-[#A88B58]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#A88B58]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-7 h-7"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 9l10.5-3m0 6.553v3.75a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.632 2.163l-1.32.377a1.803 1.803 0 11-.99-3.467l2.31-.66a2.25 2.25 0 001.632-2.163zm0 0V2.25L9 5.25v10.303m0 0v3.75a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.632 2.163l-1.32.377a1.803 1.803 0 01-.99-3.467l2.31-.66A2.25 2.25 0 009 15.553z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-[17px] font-medium text-[#544A40] mb-5 font-serif tracking-widest">
                    それぞれの目的で
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[15px] leading-loose text-[#6B5F54]">
                    趣味で好きな曲を弾きたい方、基礎から始めたい方、学校や保育の伴奏に取り組みたい方など、目的に合わせて内容を調整します。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
